00:38:04.974 --> 00:38:08.914
hematopathology, for example, sarcoma pathology, or salivary gland

636
00:38:08.994 --> 00:38:12.613
tumors that are usually diagnosed in an iterative process.

637
00:38:13.914 --> 00:38:16.594
Obviously, we are not the only ones working on this.

638
00:38:17.334 --> 00:38:21.114
This is just some very brief examples from the current literature.

639
00:38:22.034 --> 00:38:26.033
This is TissueLab, a preprint that's focusing on

