00:40:00.974 --> 00:40:04.554
important to consider. The more complex your models get,

668
00:40:04.874 --> 00:40:08.854
the larger your models get, and the more complex information and additional models

669
00:40:09.054 --> 00:40:11.614
you include into your agentic AI workflow,

